### Settings Page (`/admin/oracle/settings`)
- **Soul Prompt** editor with version history
- **Model Config**: 3-tier fallback chain, temperature/top-p sliders, max tokens, streaming toggle
- **Quota Limits**: Per-tier daily/monthly/max-per-session quotas
- **Operational Controls**: Kill switch with CONFIRM dialog, crisis response, fallback response D

### Categories Page (`/admin/oracle/categories`)
- Sortable table with icon, name, slug, color swatch, active toggle, display order
- Create/Edit dialog with emoji picker, hex color input + color picker, auto-slug generation
- Toggle active/inactive via `update` mutation (soft deactivation)

### Templates Page (`/admin/oracle/templates`)
- Tab bar filtering by category (All + each active category with count)
- Table showing question text, short label, 3rd-party badge, active toggle, display order
- Create/Edit dialog with category selector, third-party toggle with explanation panel

### Follow-ups Page (`/admin/oracle/follow-ups`)
- Template selector dropdown
- Follow-up cards with question type badge, required badge, active toggle
- Inline options editor for single_select / multi_select types (pill UI with hover edit/delete)
