## API Alignment

All admin pages use the correct Convex function names:

| Frontend Call | Backend Function |
|---|---|
| `api.oracle.categories.create` | `categories.create` |
| `api.oracle.categories.update` | `categories.update` |
| `api.oracle.categories.listAll` | `categories.listAll` |
| `api.oracle.templates.create` | `templates.create` |
| `api.oracle.templates.update` | `templates.update` |
| `api.oracle.templates.listAll` | `templates.listAll` |
| `api.oracle.followUps.createFollowUp` | `followUps.createFollowUp` |
| `api.oracle.followUps.updateFollowUp` | `followUps.updateFollowUp` |
| `api.oracle.followUps.createOption` | `followUps.createOption` |
| `api.oracle.followUps.updateOption` | `followUps.updateOption` |
| `api.oracle.followUps.deleteOption` | `followUps.deleteOption` |
| `api.oracle.injections.saveCategoryContext` | `injections.saveCategoryContext` |
| `api.oracle.injections.saveScenarioInjection` | `injections.saveScenarioInjection` |
| `api.oracle.injections.listAllCategoryContexts` | `injections.listAllCategoryContexts` |
| `api.oracle.injections.getScenarioInjection` | `injections.getScenarioInjection` |

